>>>>>>> # Starting up a Diabetes UK local group
>>>>>>> Diabetes UK is the leading UK charity that cares for, connects with
and campaigns alongside people with or at risk of diabetes. Our work in
communities across the UK would not be possible without the fantastic support
of our local groups which are an integral part of the organisation.
>>>>>>> By setting up a local group you will be part of our network across the
